# vs-scale ### VapourSynth (de)scale functions
Wrappers for scaling and descaling functions. You can find support in the [IEW Discord server](https://discord.gg/qxTxVJGtst).

## How to install Install `vsscale` with the following command: ```sh $ pip install vsscale ``` Or if you want the latest git version, install it with this command: ```sh $ pip install git+https://github.com/Irrational-Encoding-Wizardry/vs-scale.git ```
info.name: vsscale
